    <li><strong>Sludge and Water Removal:</strong> Complete three-phase separation of solids, water, and clean diesel in a single pass</li>
    <li><strong>High Separation Efficiency:</strong> Removes particles down to <strong>1 micron</strong> and all free water</li>
